    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a fighter, you gain the following class features.</p><h3>Hit Points</h3><p><strong>Hit Dice:</strong> 1d10 per fighter level<br /><strong>Hit Points at 1st Level:</strong> 10 + your Constitution modifier<br /><strong>Hit Points at Higher Levels:</strong> 1d10 (or 6) + your Constitution modifier per fighter level after 1st</p><h3>Proficiencies</h3><p><strong>Armor:</strong> All armor, shields<br /><strong>Weapons:</strong> Simple weapon, martial weapons<br /><strong>Tools:</strong> Choose one type of artisan's tool<br /><strong>Saving Throws:</strong> Strength, Constitution<br /><strong>Skills:</strong> Choose two from Acrobatics, Animal Handling, Athletics, History, Insight, Intimidation, Perception, and Survival</p><h1>Fighter Advancement</h1><table><thead><tr><th>Level</th><th>Proficiency Bonus</th><th>Features</th><th>Maneuvers Known</th><th>Superiority Dice</th><th>Superiority Size</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>1st</td><td>+2</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.IAxMIYzZbgzPRgZc]{Fighting Style}, @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.YsqyL9TutuDYy6Pi]{Second Wind}</td><td>—</td><td>—</td><td>—</td></tr><tr><td>2nd</td><td>+2</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.9OwW6R0yZc6vW9go]{Action Surge (one use)}, @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.GT5M3hT8Bj34TRH0]{Combat Superiority}</td><td>1</td><td>3</td><td>d6</td></tr><tr><td>3rd</td><td>+2</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.fawnkxUWsQF1Y3Xp]{Martial Archetype}</td><td>1</td><td>3</td><td>d6</td></tr><tr><td>4th</td><td>+2</td><td>Ability Score Improvement</td><td>3</td><td>4</td><td>d6</td></tr><tr><td>5th</td><td>+3</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.BPti7E0u0iuClFhV]{Extra Attack}, @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.YsqyL9TutuDYy6Pi]{Improved Second Wind}</td><td>3</td><td>4</td><td>d8</td></tr><tr><td>6th</td><td>+3</td><td>Ability Score Improvement</td><td>3</td><td>4</td><td>d8</td></tr><tr><td>7th</td><td>+3</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.vMN307KrRFKiSxFI]{Know Your Enemy}, Martial Archetype Feature</td><td>5</td><td>5</td><td>d8</td></tr><tr><td>8th</td><td>+3</td><td>Ability Score Improvement, @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.iEgIHhZiMmeHSjO6]{Resolute}</td><td>5</td><td>5</td><td>d8</td></tr><tr><td>9th</td><td>+4</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.EcdImxrhSRvhbBIl]{Indomitable (one use)}</td><td>5</td><td>5</td><td>d8</td></tr><tr><td>10th</td><td>+4</td><td>Martial Archetype Feature</td><td>7</td><td>5</td><td>d8</td></tr><tr><td>11th</td><td>+4</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.wu77U4NBDGyxEEXK]{Extra Attack (2)}, @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.YsqyL9TutuDYy6Pi]{Improved Second Wind}</td><td>7</td><td>5</td><td>d10</td></tr><tr><td>12th</td><td>+4</td><td>Ability Score Improvement, @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.iEgIHhZiMmeHSjO6]{Resolute Improvement}</td><td>7</td><td>5</td><td>d10</td></tr><tr><td>13th</td><td>+5</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.EcdImxrhSRvhbBIl]{Indomitable (two uses)}</td><td>7</td><td>5</td><td>d10</td></tr><tr><td>14th</td><td>+5</td><td>Ability Score Improvement, Refined Combat Style</td><td>7</td><td>5</td><td>d10</td></tr><tr><td>15th</td><td>+5</td><td>Martial Archetype Feature, @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.iDzzqYLJ7h2nLwCc]{Relentless}</td><td>9</td><td>6</td><td>d10</td></tr><tr><td>16th</td><td>+5</td><td>Ability Score Improvement</td><td>9</td><td>6</td><td>d10</td></tr><tr><td>17th</td><td>+6</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.9OwW6R0yZc6vW9go]{Action Surge (two use)}, @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.EcdImxrhSRvhbBIl]{Indomitable (three use)}, @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.YsqyL9TutuDYy6Pi]{Improved Second Wind}</td><td>9</td><td>6</td><td>d12</td></tr><tr><td>18th</td><td>+6</td><td>Martial Archetype Feature</td><td>9</td><td>6</td><td>d12</td></tr><tr><td>19th</td><td>+6</td><td>Ability Score Improvement</td><td>9</td><td>6</td><td>d12</td></tr><tr><td>20th</td><td>+6</td><td>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.HcMQpMWGb9bvBAwr]{Extra Attack (3)}, @UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.class-and-subclass-features.Item.Nk2ZC8LF5f7rUfO8]{Weapon Master}</td><td>9</td><td>6</td><td>d12</td></tr></tbody></table><h1>Martial Archetypes</h1><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.HhtdWPMvEOwv13uq]{Arcane Archer}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.wpbLIDolTNbJ2BwN]{Banneret}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.tX5WuVsAuc22vQJ1]{Cavalier}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.Zp9Me2GPK0MfbyuU]{Champion}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.AkSS6Ck8sCCSVHns]{Echo Knight}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.cWNUJjNca3Vpqltz]{Eldritch Knight}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.Uhw4D3IPLadEICuJ]{Psi Warrior}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.EBRr5DSC8Oyolb08]{Rune Knight}</p><p>@UUID[Compendium.materia-dnd.subclasses.Item.uFP0ELpknbxwhcfo]{Samurai}</p><h1>Multiclassing</h1><p>Should you wish to mulitclass into the fighter class, the prerequisites and proficiencies gained are listed below.</p><blockquote><h3>Fighter Multiclassing Prerequisites</h3><p><strong>Ability Score Minimum:</strong> As a multiclass character, you must have at least a Strength or Dexterity score of 13 to take a level in this class, or to take a level in another class if you are already a fighter.</p></blockquote><blockquote><h3>Fighter Multiclassing Proficiencies</h3><p><strong>Proficiencies Gained:</strong> If fighter is not your initial class, here are the proficiencies you gain when you take your first level as a fighter: light armor, medium armor, shields, simple weapons, martial weapons.</p></blockquote>",
